<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Consummation" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Consummation,</orth> end, death: <cit><quote>'tis a c. devoutly to be wished,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.1.63" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 1, 63</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>burning, scalding, stench, c.</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 4.6.131" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 6, 131</bibl></cit> (Ff <emph>consumption</emph>). <cit><quote>quiet c. have,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.280" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 280</bibl></cit>.
